    cabinetSupplyChainPara: "Bentwood Luxury Kitchens in Lake Forest, Drury Design in Glen Ellyn, and Insignia Kitchen in Barrington serve the North Shore luxury tier. Semi-custom comes in through Studio 41 on Elston and Airoom in Lincolnwood. Chicago-area IKEA stores in Bolingbrook and Schaumburg supply the bungalow-belt SEKTION market. Local shops including Danny Oakley Cabinet in Palatine and Acorn Kitchens in Wilmette build one-off custom pieces on 10-14 week lead times.",
